#: ../../build123d/docs/location_arithmetic.rst:9
msgid "For the following use the helper function:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../build123d/docs/location_arithmetic.rst:21
msgid "**Positioning at a location**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../build123d/docs/location_arithmetic.rst:34
msgid "**Positioning on a plane**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../build123d/docs/location_arithmetic.rst:47
msgid "Note: The ``x``-axis and the ``y``-axis of the plane are on the ``x``-axis and the ``z``-axis of the world coordinate system (red and blue axis)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../build123d/docs/location_arithmetic.rst:50
msgid "Relative positioning to a plane"
msgstr ""

#: ../../build123d/docs/location_arithmetic.rst:52
msgid "**Position an object on a plane relative to the plane**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../build123d/docs/location_arithmetic.rst:70
msgid "The ``X``, ``Y``, ``Z`` components of ``Pos(0.2, 0.4, 0.1)`` are relative to the ``x``-axis, ``y``-axis or ``z``-axis of the underlying location ``loc``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../build123d/docs/location_arithmetic.rst:73
msgid "Note: ``Plane(loc) *``, ``Plane(face.location) *`` and ``loc *`` are equivalent in this example."
msgstr ""

#: ../../build123d/docs/location_arithmetic.rst:75
msgid "**Rotate an object on a plane relative to the plane**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../build123d/docs/location_arithmetic.rst:91
msgid "The box is rotated via ``Rot(Z=80)`` around the ``z``-axis of the underlying location (and not of the z-axis of the world)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../build123d/docs/location_arithmetic.rst:94
msgid "More general:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../build123d/docs/location_arithmetic.rst:110
msgid "The box is rotated via ``Rot(20, 40, 80)`` around all three axes relative to the plane."
msgstr ""

#: ../../build123d/docs/location_arithmetic.rst:112
msgid "**Rotate and position an object relative to a location**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../build123d/docs/location_arithmetic.rst:129
msgid "The box is positioned via ``Pos(0.2, 0.4, 0.1)`` relative to the location ``loc * Rot(20, 40, 80)``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../build123d/docs/location_arithmetic.rst:131
msgid "**Position and rotate an object relative to a location**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../build123d/docs/location_arithmetic.rst:148
msgid "Note: This is the same as ``box = loc * Location((0.2, 0.4, 0.1), (20, 40, 80)) * Box(0.2, 0.2, 0.2)``"
msgstr ""
